{"tid":2181114,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中國銀行 (3988) ：不派中期息","createTime":"2020-08-30T11:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T02:25:23.000Z","uid":66271,"like":33,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9fd7f992de99fac9e34e55adfe374e8402b3410a","tid":2181114,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T11:08:59.000Z","msg":"中國銀行(03988)公布，2020年1至6月股東應享稅後利潤1,009.17億元人民幣(下同)，按年減少11.51%；基本每股收益0.32元；不派息。<br />\n<br />\n期內營業收入2,869.83億元人民幣，按年增加3.72%，其中淨利息收入增加8.37%，至1,968.95億元。<br />\n<br />\n截至2020年6月30日，核心一級資本充足率11.01%；減值貸款率1.42%；貸款撥備率3.13%。不良貸款總額1,983.82億元，比上年底增加201.47億元，不良貸款率1.42%，比上年底上升0.05個百分點，貸款減值準備餘額3,699.12億元，比上年底增加439.89億元。不良貸款撥備覆蓋率186.46%。"},{"pid":"6ea8c681078e490f437cceac856853530f75c6f9","tid":2181114,"uid":107470,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T11:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />洗唔洗隻隻開一個post"},{"pid":"4274a80ce47c870872ad0d33980010b5cd5e9afb","tid":2181114,"uid":198008,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T11:12:24.000Z","msg":"不嬲都唔派中期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ab125742812c9f47763b83fa4f1128460e0929","tid":2181114,"uid":35623,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"4274a80ce47c870872ad0d33980010b5cd5e9afb","tid":2181114,"uid":198008,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T11:12:24.000Z","msg":"不嬲都唔派中期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T11:14:37.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係得一次末期息"},{"pid":"1608631021151d2f6f6142aea9efbf8fe921a256","tid":2181114,"uid":173666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T11:14:59.000Z","msg":"勝預期"},{"pid":"f0936a1b5488a8bd7189f5f27e627346c9857745","tid":2181114,"uid":247298,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T12:47:53